Package: hunspell
Type: Package
Title: Hunspell Spell Checker
Version: 0.1
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Description: A spell checker and morphological analyzer library and program
    designed for languages with rich morphology and complex word compounding or
    character encoding.
